		<td><b>MediaWiki?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As a small experiment, I've installed MediaWiki on my server and imported a few of the main pages. It doesn't yet make use of any of the more 'advanced' features (such as categories and templates), but it does support user accounts (password-protected, no less) and a more friendly interface.
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdevwiki.ath.cx/">http://nesdevwiki.ath.cx/</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Comments are welcome - if it is decided to migrate to MediaWiki (most likely manually, as there do not appear to be any auto-import scripts and much of the markup is different), the database on my server could be easily transferred onto this site.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


